---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About — Liz Myers" current="about">
  <section class="measure" style="padding-top: var(--space-5);">
    <p class="placard" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">About / Wall Text</p>
    <h1 style="font-weight: 300; font-size: var(--fs-display); line-height: 1.05; margin-bottom: var(--space-5);">
      I prototype emerging technology and ship real products with it.
    </h1>
    <p class="tldr__body">
      I build AI experiences — daily. Right now: Gemini for inference, Claude for development, Astro for web, AIY for hardware. When a new tool arrives, I ship something with it within days.
    </p>

    <h2 style="margin-top: var(--space-6); margin-bottom: var(--space-3);">What I do</h2>
    <ul class="tldr__body">
      <li><strong>Build working prototypes fast</strong> — Blue Plaques, LingoWise, Kenny, this site</li>
      <li><strong>Translate AI for creative leaders</strong> — CMOs, founders, teams who need to see it to believe it</li>
      <li><strong>Ship real products</strong> — not just demos, things people use</li>
      <li><strong>Give outstanding live demos and presentations</strong> — I read the room, translate on the fly, and make complex things click</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="margin-top: var(--space-6); margin-bottom: var(--space-3);">Where I'm useful</h2>
    <ul class="tldr__body">
      <li>Creative agencies adopting AI</li>
      <li>Frontier AI companies needing developer advocates who ship</li>
      <li>Teams translating emerging tech for business leaders</li>
      <li>Live presentations — I make new technology obvious to the room</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="margin-top: var(--space-6); margin-bottom: var(--space-3);">Background</h2>
    <p class="tldr__body">
      RISD-trained. I speak five languages (English, German, Spanish, French, Italian) and hold dual UK/US citizenship. London, New York, Barcelona, Paris — all viable.
    </p>
    <p class="tldr__body" style="margin-top: var(--space-4);">
      <strong>Currently exploring:</strong> Generative media, AI + creative workflows, hardware + ambient intelligence.
    </p>

    <p class="tldr__body" style="margin-top: var(--space-6);">
      Want to work together? <a href="mailto:hello@lizm.dev">hello@lizm.dev</a>
    </p>
  </section>
</Base>
